To create a YouTube account, you actually need a Google account (because YouTube is owned by Google). Here’s how you can do it step by step:

1. Create a Google Account
Go to: https://accounts.google.com/signup
Enter your details:
Name
Username (this will be your Gmail address)
Password
Click Next
Add your phone number (for verification)
Enter the verification code sent to your phone
Fill in other details (birthday, gender)
Agree to Google’s terms

✅ Now your Google account is ready.

2. Sign in to YouTube
Go to https://www.youtube.com
Click Sign In (top right corner)
Enter your Google email and password
3. Create a YouTube Channel (Optional but important)

If you want to upload videos:

Click your profile icon (top right)
Click Create a Channel
Choose your channel name
Click Create
Done!

Now you can:

Watch videos
Like, comment, subscribe
Upload your own videos

